Backport of upstream regex fixes for GHSA-7wwv-vh3v-89cq (highlight.js
ReDoS in many language grammars; fixed upstream in 10.4.1, commit
373b9d862401162e832ce77305e49b859e110f9c).

Only regex-level changes are ported, and only for files that exist in
9.18.5 with a recognizably-equivalent vulnerable regex. Files where the
9.x grammar has diverged structurally from the 10.x fix are skipped.

